## Type Mapping (C -> Lean4)
- unsigned int -> UInt32 (wrapping)
- int -> Int32 or Int (for pure math, prefer Int for provability)
- int* + length -> Array Int
- char* -> Array UInt8 or String
- bool/int-as-bool -> Bool
